COPS have launched a manhunt for two men who presented
themselves as municipal employees and then robbed the family of their jewellery
in Makhado Louis Trichardt.According to police spokesperson Constable Tshifhiwa
Radzilane the first two suspects allegedly entered the premises at Eltivillas in
Louis Trichard, wearing blue overalls pretending to be on duty checking water
meters in the area. They then left after telling the victims that they would return
